hy pMifq! (AwpxI AwjIvkw dI ^wqr jjmwnW nUM piq-Awaux vwsqy ivAwh Awidk simAW dy SuB muhUrq l`Bx dw) JUT nwh bol[ s`c bolxw cwhIdw hY[
