(pMifq) vyd (Awidk Drm-pusqkW) nUM (jIvn dI AgvweI vwsqy) nhIN ivcwrdw, (ArQ qy krm kWf Awidk dI) bihs nUM hI pVHdw hY[
(ies qrHW sMswr-smuMdr dIAW ivkwr-lihrW ivc fu`bw rihMdw hY), jyhVw mnu`K Awp fu`ibAw rhy auh Awpxy (bIq cuky) bzurgW nUM (sMswr-smuMdr ivcoN) ikvyN pwr lMGw skdw hY?
